# Color Auto Detailing - Local Development

## Environment Setup

Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your values:

```
# API Configuration
PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:3001/api
API_URL=http://localhost:3001/api

# Contact form email (Resend)
RESEND_API_KEY=
CONTACT_TO_EMAIL=admin@colorautodetailing.com
CONTACT_FROM_EMAIL=no-reply@colorautodetailing.com

# Database (if using a backend)
# DATABASE_URL=

# Authentication
# JWT_SECRET=
```

## Notes

- `PUBLIC_*` variables are exposed to the browser
- Other variables are server-side only
- Never commit `.env.local` with real credentials
